Personal Finance Tracker
 
A simple app to track income & expenses
 
Features:
 
Add/Edit/Delete Transactions
 
Use objects & arrays (map, filter, find)
 
Practice immutability with spread operator
 
Categorize Transactions (Food, Rent, etc.)
 
Use enums/objects to store categories
 
Object shorthand, destructuring
 
Calculate Balance & Summaries
 
Use reduce to calculate totals
 
Handle edge cases with optional chaining & nullish coalescing
 
Save Data in LocalStorage
 
Learn JSON.stringify / JSON.parse
 
Understand persistence
 
Filter by Date Range
 
Practice array methods, conditionals
 
Export Data as JSON
 
Handling objects, modularizing logic